definition: mark/sign/label/to mark with a symbol, label, lettering etc/to bear (a brand name, registration number etc)/prize/award/bid/target/quota/(old) the topmost branches of a tree/visible symptom/classifier for military units
to record/to note/to memorize/to remember/mark/sign/classifier for blows, kicks, shots

chao1 wen2 ben3 biao1 ji4 yu3 yan2

sentences.english: It's fickle and full of angle brackets.
sentences.chinese: 它多變，而且還會充滿標記符號。

sentences.english: Memory allocation failures should reduce the use of this flag.
sentences.chinese: 如果內存分配失敗過多，應該減少這個標記的使用。

sentences.english: The results showed that there were plenty distributions of the labelled terminals within many pontine nuclei and medullary nuclei.
sentences.chinese: 結果觀察到雙側的許多核團均有順行標記終末出現。

sentences.english: It marks a one in each of those spots.
sentences.chinese: 它會標記每一個數字對應的位置。

sentences.english: Using a grease pencil or equivalent, make alignment marks on the glass and body.
sentences.chinese: 使用油筆或其它等同物，在玻璃與車體上作出標記。

sentences.english: Three portfolio units-internally set and marked. Work based learning evidence.
sentences.chinese: 三個內部單位組合設置和標記。

sentences.english: The other 5 percent is represented by supplemental plasticizers, motor oil and chemical marker.
sentences.chinese: 另外5%則是輔助可塑劑，馬達油和化學標記物。

sentences.english: An error marker appears on the project we are working on.
sentences.chinese: 我們正在工作的項目上會出現一個錯誤標記。

sentences.english: Besides adding text, you can add tags and hyperlinks to the note.
sentences.chinese: 除文本外，還可以在便籤中添加標記和超鏈接。

sentences.english: Frosted slides are sandblasted for marking specimens.
sentences.chinese: 磨砂的載玻片經噴砂處理以標記標本。

sentences.english: Using in situ end labelling, the authors demonstrated for the first time that this change belonged to apoptosis.
sentences.chinese: 經原位末端標記，首次證明本病的這種病變屬於凋亡。

sentences.english: Indicate by a check mark whether the registrant has filed all reports required.
sentences.chinese: 用對鉤標記登記者是否提交了所需報告。

sentences.english: It was signed with a different mark.
sentences.chinese: 它是用一個不同的標記簽字的。

sentences.english: A radiographic marker is received within the sealed inorganic metallic cylinder.
sentences.chinese: 在所述密封的無機金屬圓筒內置入射線照像標記物。

sentences.english: Forget growth marks scratched in pencil on the kitchen wall.
sentences.chinese: 廚房牆壁上用鉛筆畫下的身高標記已經成爲歷史。

sentences.english: A representation form for marked proper-prefixed tree in GUI is given.
sentences.chinese: 並給出真前綴標記樹的一種GUI表現方式。
